Open Warnings
-------------

 * 1007: Fix sets with * at the end of the string.

Pending Enhancements
--------------------

 * 1003: Add support for Perl-like \d.
 * 1004: Add support for Perl-like \w.
 * 1005: Add support for multiline strings ($ match the
   end of the string or a \n).
 * 1009: Refactor so that the source string can be a
   scather-gather list (a list of pointer+size pairs,
   or something like that).

Closed
------

 * 1000: Add support for sets (needs big refactoring)
